    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sorry, Wrong Door</strong> <strong>Demo </strong>is a thrilling  experience,  where you  are trapped inside a haunted castle. But this is no ordinary castle an all-powerful demon roams its halls, and the only way out is to defeat it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Face Terrifying Bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179320/extras/2b8d8eda28cfebd7d61992a59a6b5574.poster.avif?t=1749972486\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179320/extras/2b8d8eda28cfebd7d61992a59a6b5574.webm?t=1749972486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179320/extras/2b8d8eda28cfebd7d61992a59a6b5574.mp4?t=1749972486\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a procedurally generated nightmare filled with terrifying monsters, cunning traps, and deadly surprises at every turn. scavenge for weapons, find keys, and fight to survive as the castle prepares new surprises for you. The clock is ticking, and the demon is watching. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Experience Unique Adventures</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179320/extras/aa7621edc7b5da1db7a750b70de27c38.poster.avif?t=1749972486\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179320/extras/aa7621edc7b5da1db7a750b70de27c38.webm?t=1749972486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179320/extras/aa7621edc7b5da1db7a750b70de27c38.mp4?t=1749972486\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Face powerful bosses and claim unique weapon rewards. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Experience pulse pounding moments of horror: from shadowy jump scares to frantic zombie chases. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Uncover the mystery, conquer the demon, and escape... or be trapped forever.</p></li></ul>",
